description:
Disney Star Wars has always had a strong bias in its writing and the Acolyte is no exception. But in their hubris to constantly belittle men - it sometimes ends up making the writer's pet stand-in characters look hilarious inept.

#starwars #disneystarwars #theacolyte
title: Star Wars The Acolyte is Garbage part 8  #starwars #theacolyte
